me events show evidence that a portion of the ions\nhave been further stripped of electrons; such events are smaller and tend to\ncluster late in the solar cycle.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 29 Sep 2015 20:57:33 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 7 Nov 2015 21:19:56 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 29 Nov 2015 22:01:12 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Wed, 20 Jan 2016 17:18:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-01-21"}
