s of the Chandrasekhar-limit. It further argues\nfor a possible second standard candle, which has many far reaching\nimplications.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 30 Sep 2015 04:15:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-10-02"}
