o investigates the\ndependence of the statistical convergence of PDF model parameters, goodness of\nfit and skewness on the data sample size. It is shown that the minimum lengths\nof data intervals required for the robust estimation of parameters is scale,\nprocess and model dependent.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 30 Sep 2015 11:44:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-10-01"}
